text: Oedudes spectabilis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Dru Drury in 1782. It is known from Colombia, Mexico and Panama.BioLib.cz - Oedudes spectabilis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1782
